{"serial": "49002", "department_serial": 47, "code": "AC6012", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Accounting Research in the Capital Market", "ch": "資本市場會計"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Lu, Chia-Chi"], "ch": ["盧佳琪"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["5", "6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "509"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 20, "department": {"ch": "會計研究所碩士班", "en": "Msc of Accounting"}, "system": {"ch": "碩士班", "en": "Master Programs"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 12, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "培養學生結合與運用會計學術理論，會計專業知識與現代資訊科技技術，進行資本市場中的財務資訊取得，解讀與分析。本課程強調理論基礎的學習，實務現象的瞭解，科技技術的應用，期使學生具有回應當前資本市場上各資訊使用者的會計資訊需求與分析會計資訊的能力。", "en": "This course aims to equip students with the ability to integrate and apply accounting theories, professional knowledge, and modern information technology to acquire, interpret, and analyze financial information in capital markets. The course emphasizes learning theoretical foundations, understanding practical phenomena, and applying technological tools, with the goal of enabling students to meet the accounting information needs of various users in the current capital markets and to develop strong skills in analyzing accounting information."}, "outline": {"ch": "本課程內容涵蓋該領域的相關實務、理論、研究方法和實證發現。此外，課程還將探討會計資訊對會計實務和資本市場發展的角色和影響。", "en": "This course will cover the relevant practices, theories, research methodologies, and empirical findings that form the foundation of this field. Additionally, the course will explore the role and implications of accounting information for accounting practice and capital market development."}, "textbook": {"ch": "Lecture Notes and Papers", "en": "Lecture Notes and Papers"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "60", "en": "60"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "口頭報告與討論 （組）20％\n組內自評         